						<h4>Tia Glista</h4>
												<p>Tia Glista is a critic and PhD candidate in Toronto. She researches and writes on gender, feminism, literature, film, and politics. She is a founding editor of <i><a href="http://thetorontoreview.ca/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://thetorontoreview.ca&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1767811193159000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3N5_nZ8sjIzRDexob9r0-F" class="external">Toronto Review</a></i>, a magazine forthcoming in 2026.</p>
